<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فقال:</span> من كانت ابنته تحته،<span class="c5"> ولا وقف من قوله:</span> <span class="c2">«فرددناه»</span> إلى <span class="c2">«لا يعلمون»</span>، فلا يوقف على <span class="c2">«تقر عينها»</span> لعطف ما بعده على ما قبله، ولا على <span class="c2">«تحزن»</span> كذلك، ولا على <span class="c2">«حق»</span> لحرف الاستدراك بعده؛ لأنَّه يستدرك بها الإثبات بعد النفي، والنفي بعد الإثبات <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>{لا يَعْلَمُونَ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٣]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«علمًا»</span>، وكذا <span class="c2">«المحسنين»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ أَهْلِهَا}</span> <span class="c4">[١٥]</span> ليس بوقف لفاء العطف.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{يَقْتَتِلَانِ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٥]</span> جائز،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«من عدوّه»</span> الأول.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{فَقَضَى عَلَيْهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٥]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«الشيطان»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>{مُبِينٌ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٥]</span> كاف.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{فَاغْفِرْ لِي}</span> <span class="c4">[١٦]</span> حسن.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c3">{فَغَفَرَ لَهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٦]</span> أحسن منه.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>{الرَّحِيمُ <span class="c2">(١٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٦]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«للمجرمين»</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c3">{يَتَرَقَّبُ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٨]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«يستصرخه»</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>{مُبِينٌ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٨]</span> كاف.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c3">{لَهُمَا}</span> <span class="c4">[١٩]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ <span class="c2">«قال»</span> جواب <span class="c2">«لما»</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c3">{بالأمسِ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٩]</span> حسن.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c3">{فِي الْأَرْضِ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٩]</span> جائز.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>{مِنَ الْمُصْلِحِينَ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٩]</span> تام.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c3">{لِيَقْتُلُوكَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٢٠]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ويجوز:</span> <span class="c2">«فاخرج»</span>، ولا يجمع بينهما.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>{مِنَ النَّاصِحِينَ <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[٢٠]</span> كاف.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c3">{يَتَرَقَّبُ}</span> <span class="c4">[٢١]</span> حسن.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>{الظَّالِمِينَ <span class="c2">(٢١)</span>} <span class="c4">[٢١]</span> كاف.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c3">{تِلْقَاءَ مَدْيَنَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٢٢]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ جواب <span class="c2">«لما»</span> لم يأت بعد.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>{سَوَاءَ السَّبِيلِ <span class="c2">(٢٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[٢٢]</span> كاف.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c3">{يَسْقُونَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٢٣]</span> جائز.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c3">{تَذُودَانِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٢٣]</span> كاف؛ لعدم العاطف.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c3">{مَا خَطْبُكُمَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٢٣]</span> حسن، وكذا <span class="c2">«الرعاء»</span>؛ لأنَّ ما بعده منقطع؛<span class="c5"> كأنَّه قال:</span> لم خرجتما تعريضًا لموسى في إعانتهما.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
